e mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever fears Allah, no one can harm him. Whoever fears another besides Allah, no one can benefit him.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 936 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u063a\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650\u0633\u0650 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0636\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0639\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0636 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33671,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/fudayl-many-scholars-few-wise\/","url_meta":{"origin":21067,"position":1},"title":"Fudayl on Hikmah: Many scholars but few who have wisdom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: A man said to Al-Fudayl, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cThe scholars are many.\u201d Al-Fudayl said, \u201cBut those with wisdom are few.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 8\/92 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u0644\u0644\u0641\u0636\u064a\u0644 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u00a0 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0643\u064e\u062b\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0641\u0636\u064a\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0644 8\/92 \u062d\u0644\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0648\u0644\u064a\u0627\u0621 \u0644\u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32830,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/19\/fudayl-on-fame-being-famous\/","url_meta":{"origin":21067,"position":2},"title":"Fudayl on Fame: If you can get by without being famous, do so","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you can get by without being known, do so. What is it against you if you are not praised? What is it against you that people blame you but to Allah you are praiseworthy?\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19540,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/20\/fudayl-dua-muslim-imams\/","url_meta":{"origin":21067,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Rulers: Supplicating for guidance of Muslim leaders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Dhahabi reported: Al-Fudayl ibn 'Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf I had one supplication to be answered, I would make it for no one but the ruler. If the ruler is righteous, it will lead to the righteousness of the country and the people.\u201d Source: Siyar A'la\u0304m\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21077,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/21\/fudayl-on-faith-nasihah\/","url_meta":{"origin":21067,"position":4},"title":"Fudayl on Faith: Believer is happy for others, has good will","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 21, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Fudayl ibn 'Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAdmiration is part of faith and envy is part of hypocrisy. The believer admires others and does not envy others. The hypocrite envies others and does not admire others. The believer overlooks the faults of others, admonishes\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37565,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/fudayl-lonely\/","url_meta":{"origin":21067,"position":5},"title":"Fudayl on Truth: Do not feel lonely on the path of guidance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nawawi reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cDo not feel lonely on the paths of guidance because their people are few, and do not be deceived by the great many who are ruined.\u201d Source: al-Adhka\u0304r lil-Nawawi\u0304 1\/207 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0648\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0636\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u0650\u064a\u064